## About us
RemotEmployees – outstaffing company involved in searching for remote workers for employment in major foreign projects.
## Our expectations from Motion Designer
* Confident or basic knowledge of After Effects, Adobe Premiere, Photoshop, and Illustrator 2D;
* Attentiveness and a systematic approach for meeting the challenges;
* Basic 3D editor knowledge will be an advantage;
* Pursuit to grow and develop in the direction of motion design;
* Ability to establish priorities and strictly meet customer’s requirements;
* Ability to define a clear attitude and solution concerning design;
* Distinct insight into video editing, storyboarding, and engagement with a camera.
## Basic tasks of Motion Designer
* Creation of animated visualizations;
* Creation and installation of advertising and presentation videos;
* Structure development, dynamic shot creation, and work with color circle;
* Communication with customers and fulfilling tasks in English
\* Be ready to complete a test task!
## We offer:
* Full-time;
* Five-day, 8-hour work schedule;
* On-the-job training and support for beginners (Junior/ Middle);
* Remote employment and flexible working hours
If you are not sure about your experience in **motion design**, but you are eager to learn and develop your skills, we are also ready to consider you for this position!
Just send us your CV and a [short video story](/videointerview) about yourself, and we will send you an offer within one week!
## Ready to Join?
Do not miss the chance to apply for the vacancy of a motion designer. Improve your skills and expand your experience by working on major international projects worldwide! Don’t hesitate- contact us right now!
